Class KnightOrc

java.lang.Object
moving.Moving
moving.Enemy
moving.KnightOrc
public class KnightOrc extends Enemy
The KnightOrc class represents a type of enemy called KnightOrc in the game. It extends the Enemy class and overrides some of its methods.
